# Whattsap API (via whatmate)

Api for sending whattsap message/image/document to user or group

(create an account in whatsmate.net)

### Install 
```sh
$ composer require davidknafo/whatsapp
```
### Usage

```php
$instanceId   = "YOUR_INSTANCE_ID_HERE";   (data provide from whatsmate)
$clientId     = "YOUR_CLIENT_ID_HERE";     (data provide from whatsmate)
$clientSecret = "YOUR_CLIENT_SECRET_HERE";  (data provide from whatsmate)

$whatsapp = new Whatsapp($instanceId, $clientId, $clientSecret);
```

# To Group

### For sending message 

```php
$groupAdmin  = '9721234567';  (Specify the WhatsApp number of the group creator, including the country code)
$groupName   = 'MY-GROUP';    (Specify the name of the group)
$message     = 'this is a test message'; 

$whatsapp->sendTextToGroup($groupAdmin, $groupName, $message);

```

### For sending image 

```php
$groupAdmin  = '9721234567';  (Specify the WhatsApp number of the group creator, including the country code)
$groupName   = 'MY-GROUP';    (Specify the name of the group)
$image       = 'iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAUAAAAFCAYAAACNbyblAAAAHElEQVQI12P4//8/w38GIAXDIBKE0DHxgljNBAAO9TXL0Y4OHwAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='; 

$whatsapp->sendTextToGroup($groupAdmin, $groupName, $image);
```

### For sending document 

```php
$groupAdmin  = '9721234567';  (Specify the WhatsApp number of the group creator, including the country code)
$groupName   = 'MY-GROUP';    (Specify the name of the group)
//file in base64
$doc         = '';
$fileName    = 'document.pdf';

$whatsapp->sendTextToGroup($groupAdmin, $groupName, $doc, $fileName);
```

# To User

### For sending message 

```php
$toNumber    = '9721234567';  (Specify the WhatsApp number of the group creator, including the country code)
$message     = 'hi';    (Specify the name of the group)

$whatsapp->sendTextToUser($toNumber, $message);

```

### For sending image 

```php
$toNumber    = '9721234567';  (Specify the WhatsApp number of the group creator, including the country code)
$image       = 'iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAUAAAAFCAYAAACNbyblAAAAHElEQVQI12P4//8/w38GIAXDIBKE0DHxgljNBAAO9TXL0Y4OHwAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='; 
$caption     = 'My image';

$whatsapp->sendImageToUser($toNumber, $image, $caption);
```

### For sending document 

```php
$toNumber    = '9721234567';  (Specify the WhatsApp number of the group creator, including the country code)
//file in base64
$doc         = '';
$fileName    = 'document.pdf';

$whatsapp->sendDocumentToUser($toNumber, $image, $caption);
```
